	<h3 style="text-align: center;"><b><i>What began as a small, family-owned pizzeria by the outskirts of delhi, is turning into a global franchising venture. And as the popular pizza chain is expanding outside the borders of haryana, Pan pizza's ravalising taste plays an important part in their strategy for growth.</i></b></h3>

	<p style="text-align: justify-all;">WE,Somehow are the Sources of Happiness among people.People come at our Place, share food,thoughts,views etc.We Celebrate Life,Success,Happiness...Hence We Are Nothing but the Pizza Selling Company who believes in providing best service to the customers...
		With services like free home delivery, half an hour delivery etc....Today, We are having 165 franchies across the globe...Maybe different name.. But the product quality remains the same... Today, We have a turn over of 1.6 crores across the globe.<br><br><br>

	 Also, We believe that We are the Servants and Customers are the king... Hence Providing best service is a must.... We believe in a Quality product at a reasonable cost...As Customer's Satisfaction is at the priority....
	</p>
	<h3><b> HOW IT STARTED</b></h3>
	<p style="text-align: justify-all;"> It was started in 1967, when freshly baked pizza was delivered in baskets. At that time We dont provide home delivery services..Starting from the small scale business, it has now reached its path of success...Started from the roadside vendor to taking a shop on rent for the pizza shop... to now having 165 franchies across the globe..We started providing delivery services since 1980... Our first delivery service was made through bicycle... And now, we have the best delivery service across the country...
